import React from 'react';
import { Box, Container, TextField, Button, Typography } from '@mui/material';

function Login() {
  return (
    <Container maxWidth="sm">
      <Box sx={{ 
        mt: 8,
        display: 'flex',
        flexDirection: 'column',
        alignItems: 'center'
      }}>
        <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>Admin Login</Typography>
        <Box component="form" sx={{ width: '100%' }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            label="Username"
            autoFocus
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            label="Password"
            type="password"
          />
          <Button
            type="submit"
            fullWidth
            variant="contained"
            sx={{ mt: 3, mb: 2 }}
          >
            Login
          </Button>
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default Login;
